Sharing work in progress:

localtunnel
1. npm install localtunnel -g
2. start your app
3. lt --port 3000 --subdomain arpan

ngrok
1. sign up
2. install ngrok
3. install authtoken
4. start your app
5. ./ngrok http 80

now
Quickly deploy Node.js to the cloud
1. npm install -g now
2. Create start script
3. now

